VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'reference image and voice sample. &gt;&gt; These insectoids, they are already on their way. They\'re coming. But I have a solution. Insectoids, they\'re already on their way. They\'re coming. But I have a solution.'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; These insectoids, they are already on their way. They\'re coming, but I have a solution. So in this video, I\'m going to walk you through the workflow, show you how you can set it up locally on your own computer, and then we\'re going'

