[04:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'because the model needs to know what my character should look like, right? You can connect up to four references and they don\'t need to be characters. You can also reference environments or other assets. And then you just need to create a detailed prompt in natural language describing your scene. It helps to be'

